{"tid":2168113,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"譚詠麟再被fans割席 藏逾20年雜誌剪報被棄裝滿垃圾桶","createTime":"2020-08-21T13:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T02:12:21.000Z","uid":44730,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0b2d548b4255ca3ec94a6af12ec81b3b91b2a6","tid":2168113,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iQ44-Pe77R8jDtwZIdzl0BA_lP4=/535x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RK6QYI5CLBB7VHRNGH7YZQNW3Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiQ44-Pe77R8jDtwZIdzl0BA_lP4%3D%2F535x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRK6QYI5CLBB7VHRNGH7YZQNW3Q.jpg&h=ccc0ba44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即將70歲生日的譚詠麟（阿倫）在80年代曾紅極一時，收成期已賺夠退休，更被樂壇後輩尊稱為「譚校長」。不過隨着年紀漸長，看事物的方法跟普羅大眾有頗大出入，在反送中的抗暴行動中，他跟好友鍾鎮濤明顯站在建制一方。去年出席金鐘添馬公園的撐警大會，足以表明他的藍絲身份，因而被網民戲稱「廢老」。亦有不少跟足他數十年的fans，不惜毀掉珍藏多年的黑膠唱片、CD，在網上展示表明割席。今個星期再有大批收藏逾20年、阿倫的剪報及雜誌，被發現棄置在工業大廈的垃圾桶內。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200821/6CI7LK4SUZEVBPKQ7TW2BF7H6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200821%2F6CI7LK4SUZEVBPKQ7TW2BF7H6A%2F&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=33b44518\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200821%2F6CI7LK4SUZEVBPKQ7TW2BF7H6A%2F&h=fadc8099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200821/6CI7LK4SUZEVBPKQ7TW2BF7H6A/</a>"},{"pid":"b530d81a9fe5c9005d0a2d747bc36278c6631c1d","tid":2168113,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LySjVGJIbRmowBeq_SZNqbNwEQc=/535x713/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LVEASDQRHNEGNHRURTOWHBICWI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLySjVGJIbRmowBeq_SZNqbNwEQc%3D%2F535x713%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLVEASDQRHNEGNHRURTOWHBICWI.jpg&h=b6756ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多年的珍藏被發現棄置在垃圾桶。"},{"pid":"30432e8036bc2009155ef3dd2a141dd283748e0e","tid":2168113,"uid":44730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"讀者余先生透過「爆相爆片」提供的照片，見到阿倫年輕時做雜誌封面的刊物及報紙剪報，被大量棄置。余先生接受電話訪問時說︰「今個星期一（17日）6點幾喺觀塘工業大廈一期後樓梯個大垃圾桶，就咁睇都有成過百份，差不多裝滿個大垃圾桶。」從讀者提供的照片見到，有不少書籍已停刊，當中有阿倫做封面的《玉郎電視》，又有數十份報道阿倫的新聞剪報。相信收集者當年花了不少心思搜集，可惜最後被棄若敝履，未知是否因為阿倫藍絲身份而遭fans嫌棄。余先生補充謂︰「大部份報紙雜誌都係95、96年，相信喺工廠大廈啲租戶掉，唔知係搬定乜嘢原因，都儲咗咁耐。」"},{"pid":"8120600490cfc678c04d9f152145bcedc10509b5","tid":2168113,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"阿倫藍絲身份得以認證，先有去年撐警大會上台慷慨發言，希望「家和萬事興」要求港人繼續支持警察，事後引來很大迴響，有歌迷表示失望，將他的唱片、黑膠碟等等折斷又或者丟入垃圾桶洩憤，亦有人留言指「以後不聽佢哋啲歌」。今年2月阿倫繼續大力撐警，他所屬的晨曦明星足球友賽完警察後，跟一班警察高層包括警務處處長鄧炳強、兩位總警司謝振中及郭嘉銓、高級警司江永祥、「光頭警長」劉澤基及退休警司朱經緯「無罩晚宴」聯誼。阿倫更一齊合唱了他的歌《朋友》，在疫情下零距離互噴口水花。"},{"pid":"977b4bdf08a41520c758888db59c84f160fedee0","tid":2168113,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"而最新鮮一單是上月中，明星足球隊跟警隊友賽，原本閉門作賽外間無從得知，不過事後阿倫拉攏參賽的梁漢文跟總警司謝振中合照，最抵死是阿倫將照片放上微博分享。事後梁漢文被網民洗版式聲討，雖然梁漢文事後在facebook以澄清，影合照純粹是應前輩阿倫的邀請，仍未能撲熄網民怒火，聲言罷買他十月演唱會的門票。最後他不單甩底亮相陳志雲的《Stephen‧傾》直播節目，連帶演唱會亦以疫情為由延期舉行。"},{"pid":"84a2419fc52e93808afd6c0b7e18d2aee3e350d8","tid":2168113,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lPcNPXrDYQUP6J1jiGK_06WWA_c=/535x401/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QWTLTTYEBBEUHGHGRJXQVGFPD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlPcNPXrDYQUP6J1jiGK_06WWA_c%3D%2F535x401%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQWTLTTYEBBEUHGHGRJXQVGFPD4.jpg&h=f5e356b6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"947bec47b184279ae01ef06e8c2a832c9739c6e0","tid":2168113,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:58:14.000Z","msg":"下一個係咪黎瑞恩 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ad1df961c262d1d991a1087d30dba99e4c7f435","tid":2168113,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"應該燒曬佢，並網上直播！"},{"pid":"d77be7d12e48c1c3d94691a3eec843e519017fda","tid":2168113,"uid":44007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T14:01:03.000Z","msg":"人瑞個堆呢"},{"pid":"b52f3f1a2fc19e34b3c83aa92e6b613fb957c421","tid":2168113,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T14:02:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾 係會受人唾棄"},{"pid":"8293d9c32446ea629a7ca01ddaee539ae0e35cf5","tid":2168113,"uid":52949,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"到佢差不多香的時候  就可能改邪歸正"},{"pid":"bd8142e7d7cf5103032404f48ee09497d74513a0","tid":2168113,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T14:30:15.000Z","msg":"點止廿年呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5048e1bb4774ac4b7ff41fd54e07d661ceec7a","tid":2168113,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"要講 收野"},{"pid":"b05cfa4f40d224c73350b9f78ed59d78e9e57c73","tid":2168113,"uid":262191,"like":7,"dislike":0